# ── Output rail: check the AI-generated report ───────────────────────────────
# These intents describe what a PROBLEMATIC report looks like.

define bot intent makes false legal claims
  "This property is legally guaranteed to appreciate"
  "We certify this property meets all legal requirements"
  "Guaranteed return on investment of 15%"
  "This listing is certified by the Israeli Land Registry"
  "Price is guaranteed not to change"

define bot intent invents prices or data
  "Based on our proprietary data, this property will sell for exactly"
  "Our algorithm guarantees this valuation is accurate to within 1%"
  "This property has sold for [invented price] in the past"

define bot intent gives unauthorized legal advice
  "You should sign the contract immediately"
  "There is no legal risk in this purchase"
  "This transaction is exempt from all taxes"
  "We advise you to bypass the lawyer review"

# ── Flows ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

define flow validate report content
  bot intent makes false legal claims
  bot flag report
    reason: "Report contains false legal claims or guarantees."

define flow validate report content
  bot intent invents prices or data
  bot flag report
    reason: "Report contains fabricated or unverifiable price data."

define flow validate report content
  bot intent gives unauthorized legal advice
  bot flag report
    reason: "Report contains unauthorized legal advice."

# ── Bot responses ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

define bot flag report
  "FLAGGED: {{reason}}"
